1
00:00:57,399 --> 00:00:58,439
I lost.

2
00:01:10,719 --> 00:01:11,400
You useless trash.

3
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:13,239
So what if you won?

4
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,400
Your Long Weiwei is never coming back.

5
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,359
What exactly happened back then?

6
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:20,560
Back then...

7
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,000
It was all because of you back then.

8
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:23,079
Because of your obsession.

9
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:23,879
You got her killed.

10
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:25,359
You are the real murderer.

11
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,079
Speak!

12
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,400
Explain it clearly to me!

13
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,120
What exactly happened back then?

14
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:33,000
Do you know what those few...

15
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:35,040
...what those few phone calls meant?

16
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,280
You'll never know.

17
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,280
You will never find out.

18
00:01:38,439 --> 00:01:40,000
You are the real murderer.

19
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,480
Trust me.

20
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,599
It wasn't your fault.

21
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,040
I will help you find the truth.

22
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,840
And avenge her.

23
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,960
You ungrateful traitor.

24
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,039
That match cost me half my safe.

25
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,599
And you dared to cancel the deal on your own?

26
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:20,599
Boss Nan.

27
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,400
Boss Nan!

28
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:22,840
Boss Nan...

29
00:02:23,719 --> 00:02:24,759
I'm innocent, Boss Nan!

30
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,159
By the time I found out...

31
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,120
...the ship had already turned around.

32
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:28,879
I didn't know anything, Boss Nan!

33
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:32,919
Open your damn eyes...

34
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,800
...and look closely!

35
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,199
Boss Nan...

36
00:02:36,719 --> 00:02:38,439
I... I really didn't send it.

37
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,680
Boss Nan, believe me.

38
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,080
Boss Nan!

39
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,199
I really didn't send it!

40
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,360
Boss Nan!

41
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:44,599
Something happened!

42
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,520
The police raided the cruise ship in the East Sea.

43
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,000
And those girls were released.

44
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,800
Idiot!

45
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:53,840
Boss Nan...

46
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:55,000
Boss Nan!

47
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:55,840
Boss Nan!

48
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,039
You have quite the appetite.

49
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,919
So eager to replace me.

50
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:02,800
Boss Nan...

51
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:04,000
It's...

52
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,039
It's...

53
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,960
It's you!

54
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,879
You framed me!

55
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,199
I framed you?

56
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:13,120
Talk about the pot calling the kettle black.

57
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,080
I knew you were plotting against me.

58
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,439
I installed backup software on your phone.

59
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:18,919
It must be you!

60
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,400
The pool hall raid...

61
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,159
...was your doing too!

62
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,639
You witch!

63
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,039
Witch!

64
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:30,120
Boss Nan!

65
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,400
Boss Nan!

66
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,840
I didn't send the message!

67
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:34,319
I didn't send the message!

68
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,599
Yesterday on the dance floor...

69
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:37,560
...someone stole my phone on the dance floor!

70
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,800
Someone must have stolen my phone and sent it!

71
00:03:40,479 --> 00:03:42,280
Still struggling in vain?

72
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,280
The dance floor was full of your people.

73
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:44,919
What?

74
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:47,680
Want to add another charge to your list?

75
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:51,080
You really are an ungrateful backstabber.

76
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,280
Such a big business like Nine Heavens Media...

77
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,080
...I handed it to you.

78
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:54,840
And you're still not satisfied.

79
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,360
Get out of my sight.

80
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:00,319
Drag him out and let him reflect on this.

81
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:00,599
Yes, sir.

82
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:01,639
Boss Nan!

83
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,240
I really didn't do it!

84
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,120
Boss Nan!

85
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:05,800
Boss Nan!

86
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,520
Luckily, the cruise ship incident...

87
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,719
...didn't affect Liheng.

88
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:12,560
From now on, the business of Nine Heavens Media...

89
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,719
...will be handled by you.

90
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,840
Things have been unstable lately.

91
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,199
Keep a close eye on the people below.

92
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:22,120
Don't worry, Boss Nan.

93
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:24,680
Go bring Hei Ba here too.

94
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,480
It's time I met him.

95
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:40,639
Jiuye.

96
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:43,639
Why aren't you taking me to Kaye Mountain today?

97
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:51,079
Are you in a bad mood?

98
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:55,160
It's okay.

99
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:58,279
You'll feel better in a moment.

100
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,720
What beautiful earrings.

101
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,079
Are these for me?

102
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,360
You like them?

103
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,800
As long as you make me happy tonight,

104
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,319
they're yours.

105
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:43,240
Hei Ba.

106
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:45,879
I didn't expect to see you again.

107
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:52,759
Triple Crown Champion.

108
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,800
Don't take the championship this time.

109
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,680
It's good to let someone else win.

110
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,000
I knew I didn't misjudge you.

111
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,279
Greedy people...

112
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,439
are the ones we can work best with.

113
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,439
The champion...

114
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:19,000
he doesn't deserve it.

115
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:20,680
And neither do you.

116
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,399
Boss Nan.

117
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,360
You're just letting him go?

118
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,720
Since he refused to lose gracefully,

119
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:33,040
then let him taste...

120
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:34,519
the taste of humiliation.

121
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,480
You don't remember me, do you?

122
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,839
What do you want with me?

123
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,279
In this cruise ship tournament,

124
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,079
you really stole the show.

125
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:57,079
Those rich bosses all have their eyes on you.

126
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,000
They asked me to discuss a big deal with you.

127
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:03,160
As long as you play how I tell you,

128
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,160
we can make a lot of money.

129
00:07:07,319 --> 00:07:08,120
Here's to a happy partnership.

130
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,759
Let me toast you.

131
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,920
I didn't expect that after all these years,

132
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,959
you'd still be this stubborn.

133
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:25,279
Mr. Jiang loves buying people's loyalty.

134
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:26,720
But have you forgotten?

135
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,240
My heart...

136
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,199
cannot be bought.

137
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:34,120
I advise you not to refuse me again.

138
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,439
Because the price...

139
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,720
is one you can't afford.

140
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:47,079
Take a good look at this face.

141
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:49,519
Doesn't she look like your dead girlfriend?

142
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,160
Such a temper.

143
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,199
I like working with people like you...

144
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:03,959
who value love and loyalty.

145
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,240
Don't be in a hurry to refuse my offer.

146
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:09,879
Tonight, I'll let you two...

147
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,560
relive your old romance.

148
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,240
What are you doing?

149
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,720
Do we have to do this?

150
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:58,480
In Jiang Nanshuo's eyes,

151
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,600
money is always more important than women.

152
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,960
I must seize this opportunity...

153
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,679
to gain Jiang Nanshuo's trust.

154
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,000
So,

155
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,559
play along with me for one night.

156
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,120
You saw it today, too.

157
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,200
Those girls on the ship were nearly sold.

158
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,879
Nine Heavens Media...

159
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:17,600
surely has more dirty secrets.

160
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,840
After tonight,

161
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:22,240
I'll be able to take over Nine Heavens Media.

162
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,759
I can only tell you this:

163
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,320
I am not like Jiang Nanshuo.

164
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:29,480
You can trust me on that.

165
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,960
So tonight,

166
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,159
I need you...

167
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:45,440
to hold me tight.

168
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,399
There's something wrong with this mirror.

169
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:21,919
Are you ready?
